    "htmlContent": "<h2>Core Playbook</h2>\n<p>Freja sticks explosive bolts to targets from range with Take Aim, using Quick Dash to reposition and Updraft to knock enemies out of position before finishing with a headshot.</p>\n<h2>Tactical Caveats</h2>\n<p>Her Revdraw Crossbow has real travel time and a reload window, so hitscan duelists who catch her mid-reload or mid-dash punish her before she can reset.</p>\n"
